{"tid":1146504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一段逃犯條例修訂既影片（請廣傳）","createTime":"2019-05-09T09:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T19:09:54.000Z","uid":216008,"like":82,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"547f3a8fe96cf8d016547bf8873547a31f1bad9f","tid":1146504,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"時間有限 聲線難聽 多多見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5TgBtvo5WEw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5TgBtvo5WEw&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=ad8897b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5TgBtvo5WEw</a> <br />\n小弟不材 唔係一直都留意住本地時事 對於成件事完全既來龍去脈都唔係清楚曬<br />\n但眼界至雨傘運動後 政府不斷撳住香港人嚟上 <br />\n直至近排想利用一單謀殺案 利用公義之名 去將我地香港人既人權利益放上砧板<br />\n我無法忍受政府喺市民對呢一切一無所知之下去剝削我地既權利<br />\n我唔係想紅所以先整呢段片 所以都特登開過第個account 我真係想多啲香港人知道究竟發生緊咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家廣傳 比身邊更多人知發生乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期六 立法會 約定你"},{"pid":"43cd1f0711ed81169d33263d4de8a3f52eee669f","tid":1146504,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897fc5da86b206737a83021787d563bf7732f803","tid":1146504,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6df87565d754355b44c612f293fd1f54915a16e","tid":1146504,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:21:51.000Z","msg":